sa:
  The value of → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/System/CurrentControlSet/Control/Session-Manager#CriticalSectionTimeout[`CriticalSectionTimeout`] unter the
  registry key → Windows/registry/tree/HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE/System/CurrentControlSet/Control/Session-Manager[`HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Session Manager`] specifies the amount of
  seconds that a → Windows/development/process/thread can hold a critical section. 
